summary: This is a high resolution retexture of the moons Masser and Secunda. The textures are brand new and not edited versions of the vanilla textures, the resolution is up from 512x512 (vanilla) to 2048x2048. The new textures follow the same look/style as the vanilla textures too.
descriptionHtml:
[center][img]http://img5.imageshack.us/img5/5803/moontitle.png[/img][/center]

=================
Requirements:
=================

Skyrim 1.8.151.0

=================
Description:
=================

This is a high resolution retexture of the moons Masser and Secunda. The textures are brand new and not edited versions of the vanilla textures, the resolution is up from 512x512 (vanilla) to 2048x2048. The new textures follow the same look/style as the vanilla textures too.

=================
Installation
=================

1. Extract the contents of the ZIP folder into your Data folder

=================
Un-Installation:
=================

1. Delete the files/folders associated with the mod
